---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="AI Integration Consulting | Richard Kappel" description="Custom AI systems that give your team back the hours buried in busywork. Quoting, scheduling, customer follow-up, data entry. Book a free automation audit.">

  <!-- 1. HERO -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-50/60 via-white to-white -z-10"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[800px] h-[600px] bg-brand-500/[0.04] rounded-full blur-3xl -z-10"></div>
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 pt-24 md:pt-32 pb-20">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto animate-fade-in">
          <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-[1.1] text-slate-900">
            Stop paying for software<br class="hidden md:block" /> you don't own.
          </h1>
          <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            Custom software. Built for your business. Owned by you.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-10">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary inline-flex items-center justify-center px-7 py-3.5 bg-brand-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-brand-700 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-brand-200 transition-all duration-200">
              Book a Free Audit
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-14">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-8 gap-y-4">
              <span class="font-mono text-sm text-slate-400 font-medium">Slack</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-sm text-slate-400 font-medium">QuickBooks</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-sm text-slate-400 font-medium">HubSpot</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-sm text-slate-400 font-medium">Jobber</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-sm text-slate-400 font-medium">Monday.com</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-sm text-slate-400 font-medium">Mailchimp</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-sm text-slate-400 font-medium">ServiceTitan</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-sm text-slate-400 font-medium">Salesforce</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-sm text-slate-400 font-medium">Calendly</span>
            </div>
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE AI SHIFT -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-brand-600 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-600 via-brand-700 to-brand-800"></div>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 relative z-10">
      <div class="mb-10 slide-in-up">
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">
          AI changed the game.<br class="hidden md:block" /> Most businesses haven't noticed yet.
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="slide-in-up space-y-5 text-brand-100 text-lg leading-relaxed" style="animation-delay: 0.15s">
        <p>
          Six months ago, replacing your CRM would cost $50K and take a year. Today it takes weeks. The company down the street figured that out. They cut their software bill in half and put the savings into ads, new hires, and bonuses for their team.
        </p>
        <p>
          The businesses still paying per seat, renting someone else's software, are passing those costs on to customers, have a hard time hiring talent, and attracting new business.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-white pt-4">
          The window to be early is open. It won't stay open very long.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 4. PAIN MATH — WHERE THE HOURS ARE HIDING -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-50/70">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-14 slide-in-up">
        <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-brand-600 mb-3">The Problem</p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900">Where your money goes.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="slide-in-up stat-card bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-layered border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-layered-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="flex items-baseline gap-1">
            <span class="font-mono text-5xl font-bold tabular-nums text-brand-600">$1,600</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-base text-slate-400">/mo</span>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 w-10 h-[2px] bg-brand-500"></div>
          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Gone. Every month. To companies that can raise the price whenever they want. Cancel your plan? You lose your data. Stay? You lose your money. That's $19,200 a year you'll never get back. <a href="https://www.cledara.com/blog/2025-software-spend-report" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-brand-600 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-brand-700 text-sm">Source</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="slide-in-up stat-card bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-layered border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-layered-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300" style="animation-delay: 0.1s">
          <div class="flex items-baseline gap-1.5">
            <span class="font-mono text-5xl font-bold tabular-nums text-brand-600">80</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-base text-slate-400">%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 w-10 h-[2px] bg-brand-500"></div>
          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Of features are never used. You pay for 200. You use 3. The one feature you actually need? That's the next pricing tier. So you either overpay or go without. <a href="https://www.pendo.io/resources/the-2019-feature-adoption-report/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-brand-600 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-brand-700 text-sm">Source</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="slide-in-up stat-card bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-layered border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-layered-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300" style="animation-delay: 0.2s">
          <div class="flex items-baseline gap-1.5">
            <span class="font-mono text-5xl font-bold tabular-nums text-amber-500">0</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-base text-slate-400">% yours</span>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 w-10 h-[2px] bg-amber-400"></div>
          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Of your customer-facing tools carry your name. Your booking page says Calendly. Your invoices say QuickBooks. Your support chat says Intercom. Every touchpoint reminds your customer that you rent.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>










  <!-- 5A. OWN YOUR SOFTWARE -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-14 slide-in-up">
        <h2 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 uppercase">Own your tools.</h2>
              </div>
      <div class="space-y-0 slide-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s">
        <!-- Feature 1: Custom Build -->
        <div class="service-item group border-t border-slate-200 py-8 grid md:grid-cols-[4rem_1fr_auto] gap-4 md:gap-8 items-start hover:bg-slate-50/50 -mx-4 px-4 md:-mx-8 md:px-8 transition-colors duration-200 rounded-lg">
          <span class="font-mono text-sm text-brand-600 pt-1">01</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors">Custom Build</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Software built around the features you actually use. Nothing you don't. You own it outright. No per-seat pricing. No surprise price hikes in January.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="font-mono text-xs text-brand-600 bg-brand-50 px-3 py-1 rounded-full whitespace-nowrap self-start">Own it outright</span>
        </div>
        <!-- Feature 2: Your Brand -->
        <div class="service-item group border-t border-slate-200 py-8 grid md:grid-cols-[4rem_1fr_auto] gap-4 md:gap-8 items-start hover:bg-slate-50/50 -mx-4 px-4 md:-mx-8 md:px-8 transition-colors duration-200 rounded-lg">
          <span class="font-mono text-sm text-brand-600 pt-1">02</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors">White Labeled</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Your clients see YOUR name on the tools they use, not some vendor's. I build the system, you sell the service. Your margins. Your client relationship.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="font-mono text-xs text-brand-600 bg-brand-50 px-3 py-1 rounded-full whitespace-nowrap self-start">Your brand</span>
        </div>
        <!-- Feature 3: Full Migration -->
        <div class="service-item group border-t border-slate-200 py-8 grid md:grid-cols-[4rem_1fr_auto] gap-4 md:gap-8 items-start hover:bg-slate-50/50 -mx-4 px-4 md:-mx-8 md:px-8 transition-colors duration-200 rounded-lg border-b">
          <span class="font-mono text-sm text-brand-600 pt-1">03</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors">Full Migration</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Trapped in a platform that holds your data hostage? I extract everything, build the replacement, and migrate you over. Zero downtime. Zero data loss.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="font-mono text-xs text-brand-600 bg-brand-50 px-3 py-1 rounded-full whitespace-nowrap self-start">Zero data loss</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 6. BEFORE / AFTER -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-50/70">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-12 slide-in-up">
        <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-brand-600 mb-3">Results</p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900">What changes when you own it.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[1fr_auto_1fr] gap-4 md:gap-0 items-stretch slide-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.15s">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-red-100 shadow-layered relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-300 to-red-400"></div>
          <p class="text-red-500 font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">Before</p>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            {[
              { label: 'Software cost', val: '$1,600/month' },
              { label: 'Ownership', val: 'Platform owns it' },
              { label: 'Features', val: '200 you don\'t use' },
              { label: 'Pricing changes', val: 'At their mercy' },
              { label: 'Your data', val: 'Locked in their system' },
            ].map((row) => (
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-slate-100 pb-3">
                <span class="text-slate-500 text-sm">{row.label}</span>
                <span class="text-slate-900 font-medium text-sm font-mono">{row.val}</span>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Arrow -->
        <div class="hidden md:flex items-center justify-center px-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-brand-200">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"/></svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-green-100 shadow-layered relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-400 to-emerald-500"></div>
          <p class="text-green-600 font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">After</p>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            {[
              { label: 'Software cost', val: 'One payment' },
              { label: 'Ownership', val: 'You own it' },
              { label: 'Features', val: 'Only what you need' },
              { label: 'Pricing changes', val: 'Never again' },
              { label: 'Your data', val: 'On your infrastructure' },
            ].map((row) => (
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-slate-100 pb-3">
                <span class="text-slate-500 text-sm">{row.label}</span>
                <span class="text-green-700 font-semibold text-sm font-mono">{row.val}</span>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- 7. HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section id="how-it-works" class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16 slide-in-up">
        <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-brand-600 mb-3">Process</p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900">Live in 2 weeks. Not 6 months.</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-slate-500 text-lg">No IT department required. No software to learn. No disruption.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <!-- Left: Steps -->
        <div class="space-y-0">
          {[
            {
              step: '01',
              title: 'Free Software Audit (30 min)',
              desc: 'Show me what you\'re paying for. I\'ll map every tool, every subscription, every feature you use and don\'t use. You leave knowing exactly where the waste is and what can be replaced. Even if we never work together.',
            },
            {
              step: '02',
              title: 'I Build the Replacement (1 to 2 weeks)',
              desc: 'Custom software built around the features you actually use. Your workflows. Your branding. Your data on your infrastructure. One payment. No subscription.',
            },
            {
              step: '03',
              title: 'You Test It On Real Work',
              desc: 'I hand it over. Your team runs it alongside your current tools. I adjust until it works exactly how you need it. Nothing switches over until you\'re confident.',
            },
            {
              step: '04',
              title: 'Cancel the Subscriptions.',
              desc: 'The old tools go. The monthly payments stop. You own your software, your data, and your brand. That money goes back into your business.',
            },
          ].map((item, i) => (
            <div class={`slide-in-left py-6 ${i < 3 ? 'border-b border-slate-100' : ''}`} style={`animation-delay: ${i * 0.1}s`}>
              <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
                <span class="font-mono text-xs text-brand-500 pt-1.5 shrink-0">{item.step}</span>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">{item.title}</h3>
                  <p class="mt-1.5 text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">{item.desc}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
        <!-- Right: Code block -->
        <div class="slide-in-right">
          <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-layered-lg overflow-hidden">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-400/80"></div>
              <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-amber-400/80"></div>
              <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-400/80"></div>
              <span class="ml-2 font-mono text-[11px] text-slate-500">quote-agent.py</span>
            </div>
            <pre class="font-mono text-[13px] leading-relaxed overflow-x-auto"><code><span class="text-slate-500"># Your quote agent — built for your workflow</span>
<span class="text-purple-400">from</span> <span class="text-blue-300">agent</span> <span class="text-purple-400">import</span> <span class="text-blue-300">QuoteAgent</span>

<span class="text-slate-300">agent</span> <span class="text-slate-500">=</span> <span class="text-blue-300">QuoteAgent</span><span class="text-slate-400">(</span>
    <span class="text-amber-300">pricing</span><span class="text-slate-500">=</span><span class="text-green-300">"your_rates.csv"</span><span class="text-slate-400">,</span>
    <span class="text-amber-300">template</span><span class="text-slate-500">=</span><span class="text-green-300">"branded_quote.pdf"</span><span class="text-slate-400">,</span>
    <span class="text-amber-300">voice_input</span><span class="text-slate-500">=</span><span class="text-orange-300">True</span><span class="text-slate-400">,</span>
    <span class="text-amber-300">auto_followup</span><span class="text-slate-500">=</span><span class="text-orange-300">True</span>
<span class="text-slate-400">)</span>

<span class="text-slate-500"># Voice note from job site → branded quote</span>
<span class="text-slate-300">quote</span> <span class="text-slate-500">=</span> <span class="text-slate-300">agent</span><span class="text-slate-400">.</span><span class="text-blue-300">generate</span><span class="text-slate-400">(</span>
    <span class="text-amber-300">input</span><span class="text-slate-500">=</span><span class="text-green-300">"voice_note_0472.m4a"</span><span class="text-slate-400">,</span>
    <span class="text-amber-300">photos</span><span class="text-slate-500">=</span><span class="text-slate-400">[</span><span class="text-green-300">"site_1.jpg"</span><span class="text-slate-400">,</span> <span class="text-green-300">"site_2.jpg"</span><span class="text-slate-400">]</span>
<span class="text-slate-400">)</span>

<span class="text-slate-300">quote</span><span class="text-slate-400">.</span><span class="text-blue-300">send_to_client</span><span class="text-slate-400">()</span>  <span class="text-slate-500"># 4 min, not 45</span></code></pre>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-3 text-center text-xs text-slate-400 font-mono">Built for your business. Not a generic SaaS.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 8. PROOF / CREDIBILITY -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-50/70">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-12 slide-in-up">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900">Built by someone who ships.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="slide-in-left space-y-5 text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>My only employee is AI. That means my costs are low and yours are too.</p>
          <p>20 years building companies across 11 countries. Advising founders, startups, and SMBs on what actually moves the needle. I know what a business needs before I write a single line of code. That makes me fast.</p>
          <p>I shipped a full SaaS platform in weeks. No development team. No contractors. Just AI and a refined intuition for how businesses actually run.</p>
          <p>I run Build to Own Club, a community of founders building their own tools. Every edge case, every workaround, every win gets fed back into every system I build for you.</p>
          <div class="pt-4 border-t border-slate-200 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="font-mono text-xs text-slate-500 bg-white border border-slate-200 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">20 Years in Business</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-xs text-slate-500 bg-white border border-slate-200 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">11 Countries</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-xs text-slate-500 bg-white border border-slate-200 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">100+ Builders Community</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="slide-in-right">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden min-h-[300px]">
            <img src="/richard-kappel.jpg" alt="Richard Kappel" class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-2xl" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>



  <!-- 9. WHO THIS IS NOT FOR -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-14 slide-in-up">
        <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-brand-600 mb-3">Fit Check</p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900">This isn't for everyone.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="slide-in-left bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-layered">
          <p class="text-green-600 font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">This is for you if:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            {[
              'You know exactly what you\'d do with 10 more hours a week',
              'You\'re growing but can\'t hire fast enough',
              'You want your people doing the work that actually grows the business',
              'You\'re done throwing bodies at problems',
              'You want to own the tools you use, not rent them',
            ].map((item) => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-green-500 text-lg shrink-0">✓</span>
                <span class="text-slate-600 leading-snug">{item}</span>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="slide-in-right bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-layered">
          <p class="text-red-500 font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">This is NOT for you if:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            {[
              'You want to "experiment" with AI without a business goal',
              'You\'re looking for the cheapest option',
              'You don\'t have repeatable workflows yet',
              'You\'re not willing to embrace a slight learning curve',
              'You\'re fine with third parties controlling your data',
            ].map((item) => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-red-400 text-lg shrink-0">✗</span>
                <span class="text-slate-600 leading-snug">{item}</span>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 10. GUARANTEE -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-50/70">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="slide-in-up">
        <div class="guarantee-card bg-white rounded-xl p-10 shadow-layered text-center relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-[2px] bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-500 via-brand-600 to-brand-500"></div>
          <div class="mb-6">
            <svg class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto text-brand-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-brand-600 mb-4">Guarantee</p>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">The guarantee.</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed text-left">
            If what I build doesn't save you time, cut costs, or give you more control over your tools and data in the first month, I'll rebuild it. Free. And if you're still not satisfied, full refund. No questions. No awkwardness. I don't keep money I didn't earn.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 11. FINAL CTA -->
  <section class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden bg-brand-600">
